list.abstract: 《Finally》是安室奈美惠演唱的歌曲，由Emyli、Matthew Tishler、Felicia Barton、Ben Charles填词，Matthew Tishler、Felicia Barton、Ben Charles谱曲，收录于安室奈美惠2017年11月8日发行的专辑《Finally》中。

yingyinNormal.en: And finally, the cooked eggs.
yingyinNormal.zh: 最后，加入炒熟的鸡蛋。

yingyinNormal.en: Finally, a topping of tangy mushrooms.
yingyinNormal.zh: 最后做些香气扑鼻的蘑菇作点缀。

yingyinNormal.en: Thank you. Right. And finally, Kevin. Yes, my queen.
yingyinNormal.zh: 谢谢。好吧，最后，凯文。在，我的女王。

yingyinNormal.en: And finally, our first bunny, Officer Hopps. Parking duty. Dismissed.
yingyinNormal.zh: 最后，第一只兔子，霍普斯警官，交通协管，解散。

yingyinNormal.en: Finally, some white and black pepper and a pinch of salt. Now mix that up.
yingyinNormal.zh: 最后，再加入一些黑白胡椒粉和少许盐，把它们搅拌均匀。

yingyinNormal.en: Only a little bit. You don't want this to rise high. Finally, salt, and cold water.
yingyinNormal.zh: 一点就可以，不然就会变得很大，最后加入食盐，凉水。

yingyinNormal.en: Finally, we can't just cut ourselves off from West Africa where this disease is raging.
yingyinNormal.zh: 最后，我们不能仅仅阻断我们与疾病肆虐的西非的联系。

yingyinNormal.en: Finally, the beer. No drinking, just pour, just pour some of the beer over the fish.
yingyinNormal.zh: 最后加入啤酒。不许喝，全倒进去！把部分啤酒浇在鱼身上。

yingyinNormal.en: It gives a bit of longevity to the loaf, keeps it nice and soft. And finally, 320 ml of water.
yingyinNormal.zh: 这会让面包更持久，更漂亮，更松软，最后加入320毫升的水。

yingyinNormal.en: All right. And finally, on the wall back there is a black panel. Blinky yellow light. Do you see it? Yeah.
yingyinNormal.zh: 好，最后，后面墙上有块黑色板子，闪黄灯那里，看到没？有。

yingyinNormal.en: It's difficult to get a booth, finally, we got a small booth. We got the booth, but very few people find us.
yingyinNormal.zh: 找展位很难，最后我们终于找到一个很小的位置，但是很少人光顾。

yingyinNormal.en: Finally, we have 14 missing mammal cases. All predators. From a giant polar bear to a teensy little otter.
yingyinNormal.zh: 最后，有14起哺乳动物失踪案，全是食肉动物，从大北极熊到小水獭。

yingyinNormal.en: And, and finally when I thought you were making sexual advances in the workplace, I said no and I was not litigious.
yingyinNormal.zh: 最后当我以为你想趁工作之便占我便宜我拒绝了，但是没打算告你。

yingyinNormal.en: So you're telling me to be bored, and then bored, and finally bored again, but this time for the rest of my life.
yingyinNormal.zh: 所以你在这是告诉我要变得无聊，然后觉得无聊，最后还是无聊，但这次事关我的一生。

yingyinNormal.en: I want to show you that making bread is simple, really. You mix, knead, prove, shape, prove again, and finally bake.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我想展示给你的是，做面包真的很简单，和面，揉面，醒面，塑形，再次醒面，最后烘烤。

yingyinNormal.en: Finally, let's honor our veterans by remembering that this isn't just a job for government, it's a job for every American.
yingyinNormal.zh: 最后，让我们向我们的退伍军人致敬牢记这不仅仅是政府的事，这是每一个美国人的事。

yingyinNormal.en: Hello, I am the carwash of the future. First, soapy water. Then a rinse. And finally, a polish. Sorry, I have malfunctioned.
yingyinNormal.zh: 你好，我是未来的洗车机。首先，肥皂清洗车。然后冲洗干净。最后呢，再擦干净。对不起，我出问题了。

yingyinNormal.en: Who is this god that denies us a baby, then gets a party girl pregnant, only to have her desert the baby so that we can finally get one?
yingyinNormal.zh: 这个上帝不让我们领养孩子，却让一个狂野女怀了孕，最后抛弃自己的孩子，所以我们能收养他。

yingyinNormal.en: Finally, the line "in this room the thing you'll see" was an obvious reference to Fantastic Four member The Thing, who's made entirely of...
yingyinNormal.zh: 最后那句"此物屋内显踪迹"是很明显指向神奇四侠的石头人(The Thing) 是全部由什么组成的。

yingyinNormal.en: And then finally Frank stopped the class and said, "you two are distracting me. Go outside, have sex, and come back when you're ready to learn something. "
yingyinNormal.zh: 最后弗兰克看不下去了，停下来说道，“你们俩太让我分心了，出去，上个床，准备好学知识了再进来。”

disambiguation_list.sense_disambiguation: 表示某一动作发生的顺序是在“最后”，无感情色彩，它在句中的位置以在句首时为多。
往往表示经过一番努力或曲折的过程，常常带有较浓厚的感情色彩，也可用来表示“等候或耽误了很长时间之后才 ……”，语气比较强烈。
表示经过许多变化、困难或捉摸不定的情况之后，某事才发生，有时可与finally 互换。
